N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 333.3 - Ballot, envelopes delivered in hand

State Regulations
A military ballot shall be delivered in hand to each
military voter who personally files an application (pursuant to subdivisions 8
through 11 of section 305 of the Election Law) together with a ballot envelope
and a second envelope addressed to the Secretary of State of New York, Division
for Servicemen's Voting, Albany, New York 12231. Notes
